{
  "page": "Lord Smallwood",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\"><img alt=\"House Smallwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/50px-House_Smallwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/75px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/100px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Smallwood</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\"><img alt=\"House Smallwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/50px-House_Smallwood.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/75px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/100px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Lord of Acorn Hall\">Lord of Acorn Hall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\">House Smallwood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLady Smallwood</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Smallwood</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\">House Smallwood</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys I Targaryen\">Aerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His given name is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Smallwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212&#160;AC</a>, Lord Smallwood and his wife came to <a href=\"/index.php/Whitewalls\" title=\"Whitewalls\">Whitewalls</a> with a retinue to attend the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wedding\">wedding</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Butterwell\" title=\"Lady Butterwell\">the daughter</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Frey\" title=\"Lord Frey\">Lord Frey</a> to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ambrose_Butterwell\" title=\"Ambrose Butterwell\">Ambrose Butterwell</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kyle_the_Cat\" title=\"Kyle the Cat\">Kyle the Cat</a> tried to ingratiate himself with Lord Smallwood, as they were slightly acquainted prior to the festivities.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Smallwood's nephew broke his wrist during the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls\" title=\"Wedding tourney at Whitewalls\">wedding tourney at Whitewalls</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\">Glendon Flowers</a> was imprisoned after being accused of stealing the prize of the tourney, Ambrose's treasured <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_egg\" title=\"Dragon egg\">dragon egg</a>. When Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> publicly declared that Glendon had been falsely accused, <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">Daemon II Blackfyre</a> ordered Lords Smallwood, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Sunderland\" title=\"Lord Sunderland\">Sunderland</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vyrwel\" title=\"Lord Vyrwel\">Vyrwel</a> to fetch Glendon from the dungeons.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if Lord Smallwood suffered any punishment for the part he played in the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"Second Blackfyre Rebellion\">Second Blackfyre Rebellion</a>, which was suppressed by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Smallwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405060633\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.082 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.274 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 589/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10527/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5448/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 301/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1830/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.35 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  262.560      1 -total\n 92.02%  241.595      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.14%  239.286      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.87%   25.915     12 Templa